Jeremy,

Yes, it has been noted since the beginning of ITC experimentation that your psi abilities in seeing, feeling  and hearing increase the more you expose yourself. It is also noted that the abilities will most likely fade if you stop for a long period of time. 

I hear them from time to time without any technical means but it is usually only one word. I especially hear them if a faucet is left trickling in another room. I also catch glimpses of them in the room.... On that note, my cats are so brave. They will stand guard at my bedroom door and my kids bedroom door when they are present. As if they will not let them pass....

There is my little piece of craziness and vulnerability. LOL

Regards,

Frank R.

----- Original Message ----
From: ecuyler &lt;ecuyler@...&gt;
To: EVP-ITC@yahoogroups.com
Sent: Tuesday, February 5, 2008 9:48:32 PM
Subject: [EVP-ITC] Observation














            I have a question for those of you who have been doing this research

for a while.  Since doing the research, have you noticed an increase

in your &quot;intuitive&quot; senses?  By that I mean, has your hearing been

heightened to the point of hearing conversations when you are alone? 

Or seeing things more clearly spirit wise?  Or am I just nuts and need

to be committed?  



I had to ask.  It&#39;s a very strange thing.  These things have been

happening to me and I&#39;m wondering if you have experienced the same

thing or close to it.



Jeremy














